HTML-BBReverse 0.03
===================

HTML::BBReverse is a pure perl module for converting BBCode to HTML
and is able to convert the generated HTML back to BBCode.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Build.pl
   ./Build
   ./Build test
   ./Build install

DEPENDENCIES

  none

